<% if @animal.animal_type() == "Dog" %> <h4>Introducing Rover the Dog</h4>
<p>Rover was found on the motorway when he was only two years old.</p>
<p>He is very shy and doesn't like busy streets.</p>
<img src="Rover_Dog.jpg" alt="picture of dog" height="400px" width="500px">
<% end %>

<% if @animal.animal_type() == "Hamster" %> <h4>Fred the Hamster</h4>
<p>Fred was found last year in the Meadows.</p>
<p>He was slightly depressed and had some counselling and is much happier now.</p>
<img src="Fred_Hamster.jpg" alt="picture of hamster" height="400px" width="500px">
<% end %>

<% if @animal.animal_type() == "Rabbit" %> <h4>Bunny the Rabbit</h4>
<p>Bunny arrived in June and was found in the middle of Princes Street near Primark.</p>
<p>She was slightly traumatised but is she is very friendly.</p>
<img src="Bunny_Rabbit.jpg" alt="picture of rabbit" height="400px" width="500px">
